        <h2>Support</h2>
        <p>Need help with StitchUp Repairs? We're here to assist you.</p>

        <h3>Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
        <p><strong>How do I create a repair request?</strong><br>
        Tap the + button in the tab bar, take or select a photo of the item, describe the repair needed, set your budget and travel radius, then tap "Post Repair Request".</p>

        <p><strong>How do I apply for a repair job?</strong><br>
        Switch to "Available Jobs" on the home screen, browse nearby requests, tap one to view details, and tap "Apply for this Job".</p>

        <p><strong>How does payment work?</strong><br>
        Payments are handled directly between users via PayPal. After a job is completed, the requester can pay using the "Pay via PayPal" button, which opens a pre-filled PayPal.me link.</p>

        <p><strong>How do I set up my PayPal?</strong><br>
        Go to your Profile tab and enter your PayPal.me username. This allows others to pay you directly.</p>

        <p><strong>How do I delete my account?</strong><br>
        Go to Profile → scroll to the bottom → tap "Delete Account". This permanently removes your account and all associated data.</p>

